Facebook ko ek problem najar aai ki real time main wo notification and reactions ka show nahi kar paa rahe hai,
unhe reactions,notification and other data deliver karne main page reload karna pad rha hai,and wo isliye kyuki
they were using something called PHP, ab is problem se nipatane ke liye 2013 main facebook ke engineering team 
ne ek library banaai ye library khas thi, kyuki ye data ko real time mein dikha paa rahi thi , par is library 
ke kaam karne ka tareeka different tha, ye main DOM tree ko update nahi krti hai directly, matlab ki agar page
mein kuchh bhi change hua to directly main DOM tree update nahi hoga, is library ka khud ka ek DOM tree hai 
uska naam hai virtual DOM ye DOM tree exact copy hai real DOM tree ka, bas ek difference hai, wo hai ki jab 
bhi virtual DOM mein kuchh change hoga to sirf use change kiya jaayega jo ki change hua hai ki nahi poore 
tree ko refresh kiya jayega.


Benifits of using React to create a website
    -> very very less page relodes
    -> extreme use of components
    -> very efficient

react learn what matters 
what -> js libary to maintain frontend efficient
why ->  reactjs is more mantainble and efficient, lightweight
How -> create components and make data if you needed and change data whenever you want, react will react jab v data change hoga

when -> jb aapko thora bade level par app create krna ho jaha bhut sare components or changes ho rahi ho.   